> [schiz0](#comment_17_153dW34Ng5fVUZ5D5NcZRfAbvRQS1jYC1k): I've changed max_size to 400000 before launching the script, the first time;
> now in my data.json there are only three posts,but nothing

Have you signed it from the right panel? You can also try to reload and rebuild the database, iirc in that way even you don't sign the file, the posts will be loaded.

> [herp](#comment_1_164x9q7LJPLX4SMbhqLPraKAGZRPa2gTFe): This looks pretty good! Might need to figure out a fix for it running off the side, but I imagine you can just shrink the line lengths.

Adding this to all2.css can solve the issue:
```
  td {
    max-width: 375px;
    word-wrap: break-word;
  }
```

If you need a wider window and longer text, you can respectively change
```
.container {
    max-width: 890px;
...
```
